nodes.text: The Squib Polyanarchy was the main governing body of Skor II and of the Squib species. It was made up of several independent communities under the nominal rule of a king. The Squib king was Ebareebaveebeedee during the end of the Old Republic era and the beginning of the Imperial era. The Squib Polyanarchy's relationship with the Squib Merchandising Consortium, a Squib-wide corporation, is not known. The two may have been one and the same, they may have had different jurisdictions, or they may have overlapped.
